{"root":{"data":{"id":"dgypb3ygosg0","created":1773105121884,"text":"电饭煲"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgypb5a7u4g0","created":1773105124772,"text":"低糖饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0n30xio3k0","created":1773301966077,"text":"煮饭--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃时，P15引脚高电平持续4min\n\n开关/功能LED灯常亮，数码管显示转圈流水灯","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0omz3i7gg0","created":1773306350479,"text":"焖饭--P15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--27次，时长18min\n当NTC检测103℃，P15引脚低电平--继电器断开停止加热\n\n煮饭20min后，数码管显示15min倒计时","layout":null,"priority":2},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0orzmnduo0","created":1773306743457,"text":"保温：65-70℃\nNTC检测温度低于65℃时，P15引脚高电平10s，低电平20s--间歇加热\n高于70℃时，P15引脚低电平--停止加热\n循环\n\n保温：数码管显示计时","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb63g16w0","created":1773105126539,"text":"柴火饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ov2z7sdc0","created":1773306985840,"text":"煮饭--P15引脚高电平--继电器吸合启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，P15引脚高电平持续3min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0owqc24io0","created":1773307115047,"text":"焖饭\nP15引脚高电平32s，低电平8s--开关90次，时长1h；\nP15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--开关6次，时长4min\n当NTC检测103℃，P15引脚低电平--继电器断开停止加热","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oxl5bc800","created":1773307182119,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb6hc6x40","created":1773105127379,"text":"杂粮饭","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0ov2z7sdc0","created":1773306985840,"text":"煮饭--P15引脚高电平--继电器启动加热\n当NTC检测100℃，P15引脚高电平持续3min","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0owqc24io0","created":1773307115047,"text":"焖饭\n①P15引脚高电平32s，低电平8s--开关78次，时长52min；\n②P15引脚高电平15s，低电平25s--开关6次，时长4min；\n③P15引脚低电平持续16min\n当NTC检测103℃，P15低电平--继电器断开停止加热","priority":2,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dh0oxl5bc800","created":1773307182119,"text":"保温","priority":3,"layout":null},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgypb6zl6e00","created":1773105128483,"text":"香浓粥","layout":null},"children":[{"dat